{"code":"# 1 2 3\r\n# 1 {1 2} 2 {2 3} 3 {1 3}   -> 1:3, 2:3, 3:3\r\n# 1 (1 1 2) {1 2} (1 2 2) 2 (2 2 3) {2 3} (2 3 3) 3 (1 3 3) {1 3} (1 1 3)  -> 1:9, 2:9, 3:9\r\n\r\nn = int(input())\r\na = list(map(int,input().split()))\r\nk = int(input())\r\n\r\np = 3 ** k\r\ncnt = sum([x * p for x in a])\r\nfor i in range(k):\r\n    n += n\r\nprint(f\"{cnt\/n:.3f}\")","lang":2}